snippet.title: Damned House | Teaser Trailer | Wishlist Now on Steam
snippet.description:
"Damned House" is a horror game set in a spooky house. Explore the house, while trying to escape from very hostile creature and various dangers. There will always be a constant danger of death, do you dare to explore the house and escape from it?

________________________________________________________________________


Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2609380/Damned_House/
Discord: https://discord.gg/NhwMvSqAex
